Created the TicTacToe Game using a single array in Go language in Atom Text Editor
Pelase down the Atom Text editor from Google using https://atom.io/ link
Run the program in the command prompt in the specific path you have stored the TicTacToe file
Then run the game as go run TicTacToe.go then press enter
It will ask the human to enter the numbers from 1 to 9 indication the 3*3 table as below
---
---
---
Continue to enter until the game is either win or draw
